There is a 2nd Coney Island Sign further down east near Coney Island (Beach Area D).

There is a Coney Island sign here, and the small beach has a nice view, but the seawater on the beach has a lot of seaweed and a lot of garbage. It looks like it has been left unattended for a long time. I hope the Singapore government will send someone to clean it.
